item.title: History
item.description: About Heading Automate Everything (AE) was started in 2018 by two South African ‘boytjies’ with a passion for DevOps, automation, and ‘Cloud Native’ computing. They both earned their wings working for a variety of companies in both the United Kingdom and South Africa, and decided to bring home their talent.
